snippet.title: The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom – Official Trailer #3
snippet.description:
Watch the final pre-launch trailer for The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom, coming May 12th, only on Nintendo Switch.

Pre-order now: https://www.zelda.com/tears-of-the-kingdom/
